SCRCPY GUI WRAPPER - INSTALLATION COMPONENTS
==========================================

This installer will set up the following onto your computer:

1.  Scrcpy GUI (The visual application)
2.  ADB (Android Debug Bridge) - Used to talk to your phone.
3.  scrcpy binaries - The core mirroring engine by Genymobile.
4.  Desktop & Start Menu shortcuts.

SAFE & FREE:
All components are bundled locally. No system settings are changed except for the shortcuts and the installation folder.

CLEAN REMOVAL:
You can uninstall this application at any time via 'Add or Remove Programs' in Windows.
